creator: Mannequin
descriptionHtml: Welcome to the Mannequin fashion app. The Mannequin fashion app is a FREE fashion listing platform for store owners to display their merchandise to potential buyers. Other registered mannequin users can view the listings and contact the sellers through the app. It’s a new simplified way for fashion discovery with search and filter features basing on location, sex, size, price and age.
descriptionShort: Mannequin is a FREE fashion display platform for sellers to find new customers

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Great new attractive, login and signup screens
- Test that creation of a new account is successful
- Testing that login with the same account is successful
- Test signing out of your account successfully
- Test viewing of products, these are test products so far and will be all discarded after testing
- Testing view a single product details.
- Test updating your account details and profile image.
- Test creating a new product for sell.
